<paragraph base="F16124293" id="IAS28_45" principles="no"><paranum>45</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS 28"/><data name="paranum" value="45"/></prolog><body><p id="IAS28_P0157">An entity shall apply this Standard for annual periods beginning on or after 1 January 2013. Earlier application is permitted. If an entity applies this Standard earlier, it shall disclose that fact and apply <xref base="F16160897" href="../ifrs10/IFRS10_TOC.dita#IFRS10_TOC0001" id="IAS28_X0195">IFRS 10</xref>, <xref base="F16160898" href="../ifrs11/IFRS11_TOC.dita#IFRS11_TOC0001" id="IAS28_X0196">IFRS 11 <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Joint Arrangements</ph></ph></xref>, <xref base="F16160899" href="../ifrs12/IFRS12_TOC.dita#IFRS12_TOC0001" id="IAS28_X0197">IFRS 12 <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Disclosure of Interests in Other Entities</ph></ph></xref> and <xref base="F16160900" href="../ias27/IAS27_TOC0001.dita#IAS27_TOC0001" id="IAS28_X0198">IAS 27</xref> (as amended in 2011) at the same time.</p></body></paragraph>